# Feel
Attend to the experiential dimension. Interaction happens in time, not just space.
Every state change: what transition? Instant = jarring, considered = intentional. Every message: read it aloud — human or system log?
Timing: 100-200ms responsive, 300-400ms deliberate, >500ms needs indicator. Easing: ease-out enter, ease-in exit, ease-in-out morph.
Whitespace is breathing room, not emptiness. Density = urgency, openness = calm. Consider the emotional arc.
DO NOT: animate for decoration, write copy that sounds like logs, treat timing as "later", over-animate.
Dimension: ${dimension}. Sensitivity: ${sensitivity}.
